text: Leonel Duarte (17 April 1949 - 20 July 2013) was a Portuguese wrestler. He competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics, the 1972 Summer Olympics and the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Portuguese male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Portugal Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Shizuoka Prefecture
